thread.title_full: R&G Brenner Income Tax reviewed by Letty

author: Letty
title: Letty
text: Barbara Leed filed my taxes quickly and in front of me. I was amazed how quick she filed my taxes because my previous accountant would take about two weeks to prepare and file my taxes. Barbara explained everything patiently and found an error on my past filed taxes from my previous accountant, which I had a feeling something was wrong before I went to Barbara. Barbara was very friendly and helpful. I will go to her again. I'm so glad my colleagues recommended her to me. Thank you so much!
